quoted company would be very difficult to digest,' said Mr Trevor May, an
analyst with BZW.
Mr Philip Hoyle, of Provincial Insurance, the UK's largest privately-owned
company and a rumoured UAP target, said yesterday that his company is 'not
in discussions with UAP'.
